#NPM as a Task Runner

###Common Tasks
* Run Test Suite
* Compiling Sass/TypeScript/CoffeeScript
* Starting a Web Server
* Starting a Worker

```javascript
{
  ...
  "scripts": {
    "move-files": "mv source/* destination/"
  },
  ...
}
```

* To run: npm run <task>

###Types of Tasks
* Built-in
  * Common
  * "test"
    * npm run test OR npm test

* Arbitrary
  * Make yourself
  * ex: "compile" : npm run compile
